## Quick Start

```bash
# Install dependencies
npm install

# Copy environment variables
cp .env.example .env

# Update DATABASE_URL in .env with your PostgreSQL connection string

# Run migrations
npm run db:migrate

# Start development server
npm run dev
```

Your auth backend will be running at `http://localhost:3000`.

